stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> Draft : idea
    Draft --> Accepted : discuss,\nresolve >> threads
    Accepted --> Superseded : material change\nneeded; new SRD written
    note right of Draft
        open >> threads ok
        exploratory spikes ok
        code should not yet follow
    end note
    note right of Accepted
        code follows
        referenced by later SRDs
    end note
